WEBVTT

00:00.904 --> 00:03.839
<i>Previously on "Transformers Prime"...</i>

00:03.908 --> 00:07.590
It is paramount that we recover
the final four Iacon relics ...

00:07.591 --> 00:10.045
the Omega keys.

00:10.114 --> 00:12.047
- Keys?
- To what?

00:12.116 --> 00:15.050
The regeneration of our home planet.

00:15.119 --> 00:19.855
A tomb. One known to contain
the remains of Primes.

00:19.924 --> 00:25.928
At long last, the power of the
Primes belongs to me!

00:25.996 --> 00:29.765
Four sets of coordinates from
Alpha Trion remain encrypted.

00:29.834 --> 00:33.069
It is logical to conclude
that each corresponds

00:33.070 --> 00:36.305
to the location of
one of the Omega keys.

00:36.373 --> 00:40.509
My first creation, fashioned
from the very blood of Unicron.

00:40.578 --> 00:43.245
I call it the Dark Star Saber.

00:43.314 --> 00:45.347
The relic now!

00:45.416 --> 00:49.084
Oh, you mean this?
Finders keepers.

00:50.085 --> 00:53.085
<b>2x22 - Hard Knocks</b>

00:55.000 --> 01:01.074
Advertise your product or brand here
